Program: Free Thinking
Title: Zadie Smith
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0833ypn
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 23 Nov 2016
Zadie Smith talks dance, depicting teenage friendships and US/UK differences with Philip Dodd as her new novel Swing Time is published in Britain and BBC TV dramatises her book NW starring Nikki Amuka-Bird and Phoebe Fox. Producer: Robyn Read (Image: Zadie Smith (c) Dominique Nabokov).